ation-tier awareness.\n- **State discrepancy:** `sprint-state.json` shows 10-3 at `review`, `sprint-status.yaml` shows `verifying`. Needs reconciliation.\n- **Top action items:** Start Docker, verify 10-3, reconcile state files, then proceed to 10-4."}],"totalDurationMs":121423,"totalTokens":39788,"totalToolUseCount":16,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3021,"cache_read_input_tokens":36490,"output_tokens":276,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":3021},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
